{
  "stem": "14867.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My-- my friends who survived-- the few friends who survived-- remind me of things about my parents and about my family, which really, I'm delighted to hear.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I told you, I went two years ago for the first time back to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And just to tell you one thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I met there, a girl that went to school, to medical school in Lvov with me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was telling me wonderful stories about my-- about my family that I never knew, yes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Was I in medical school?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, because in-- in-- I never saw the Germans again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because you're talking about in-- between '41 and '43?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, at that time, you-- of course, you had-- you could work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They needed the Jews for work, and that's the reason some ghettos lasted much longer.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's say they had factories of making paper out of clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they needed people to-- to take apart all the clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And let's say the clothes that we were taking apart came from-- from dead Jews already.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'll tell you in a minute how we knew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, there were all kinds of jobs that they needed-- the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and they need workers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So if you knew someone-- and my brother's friend happened to be on the city council, on the Judenrat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- This is in Lvov?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Lvov.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he gave us permits.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he gave us permits for working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So not everybody could get it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was for my sister, my sister-in-law, and myself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since we were working, and there was a baby to take care of, they told us that my mother would be protected, that she can stay home and take care of the baby.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so that's what's happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
